note:
My name is Angelika, I am a registered member in good standing with The College of Massage Therapists of Ontario. I graduated from the Canadian College of Massage and Hydrotherapy in 2011, where I exceeded my practical experience requirements.

I has always had a passion for helping others which has led me to my career as an RMT. Since graduating I has taken additional courses to benefit my clients such as therapeutic ultrasound, kinesiology taping, cupping therapy and hot stone massage.
